  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The alien Red Falcon is back, and planning on taking over the planet Earth.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super C may refer to:\n\nSuper C (freight train), a high-speed train operated by the Atchison, Topeka and Santa Fe Railway, U.S.\nSuper C (supermarket), a Canadian grocery store chain\nSuper C class ferry, built in Germany for BC Ferries, British Columbia, Canada\nSuper C Season, a 2011 album by Nigerian rap artist, Naeto C\nSUPER ©, software used to convert (encode) or play multimedia files\nA version of the video game Super Contra that was ported to Nintendo Entertainment System\nA character developed by American singer Ciara and used to promote her album Fantasy Ride\nA junior ice hockey trophy in Ontario, Canada; see Clarence Schmalz Cup\nSuperC (Aachen), a central service building at the RWTH Aachen in Germany",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
  ]
